  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231490/extras/b2718316aa8deb0e0e644c0501863447.avif?t=1672705048\" width=420 height=108 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>About Squared</u></strong></h2>A small grid-based puzzle game where you take control of a square. Move around the blocks and walls, change gravity and overcome obstacles to reach the Exit Portal.<br><br><br>-Contains 100 Levels<br>-Beating this game can take from 35 minutes to 5+ hours, depending on how fast you are in solving the levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Controls</u></strong></h2><br><strong>~Arrow keys, W/A/S/D keys || gamepad stick, d-pad~</strong><br>    Move around blocks and walls<br><br><strong>~Space || A-button, B-button~</strong><br>    Change Gravity<br><br><strong>~P key || start button~</strong><br>    Pause Game<br><br><strong>~F key || select button~</strong><br>    Toggle Fullscreen",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231490/extras/b2718316aa8deb0e0e644c0501863447.avif?t=1672705048\" width=420 height=108 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>About Squared</u></strong></h2>A small grid-based puzzle game where you take control of a square. Move around the blocks and walls, change gravity and overcome obstacles to reach the Exit Portal.<br><br><br>-Contains 100 Levels<br>-Beating this game can take from 35 minutes to 5+ hours, depending on how fast you are in solving the levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Controls</u></strong></h2><br><strong>~Arrow keys, W/A/S/D keys || gamepad stick, d-pad~</strong><br>    Move around blocks and walls<br><br><strong>~Space || A-button, B-button~</strong><br>    Change Gravity<br><br><strong>~P key || start button~</strong><br>    Pause Game<br><br><strong>~F key || select button~</strong><br>    Toggle Fullscreen",
